.I.T. Press, 1961.6.	Forrester, J.W., Urban Dynamics, The M.I.T. Press, 1969.7.	Forrester, J.W. & Senge, P.M., “Tests for Building in System Dynamics Models”, Studies in the Management Science, Vol.14, p.209-228, 1980.8.	Legasto A. A., & Maciariello J., “System Dynamics: A Critical Review”, Studies in the Management Science, Vol.14, p.23-43, 1980.9.	McCue, T. E. & Kling J. L.,“Real Estate Returns & the Macro Economy: Some Empirical Evidence from Real Estate Investment Trust Date, 1972-1991,” The Journal of Real Estate Research, Vol.9, p.277-288, 1994.10.	Pyhrr, S. A. & Cooper, J. R., Real Estate Investme: Strategy Analysis, Decisions, p.485, 1982.11.	Roberts, E. B., (ed.), Managerial Applications of System Dynamics, Waltham, MA: Pegasus Communications, U.S.A, pp.3-35, 1978.12.	Stave, K. A.,”Using System Dynamics to Improve Public Participation in Environmental Decisions”, System Dynamics Review, Vol.18, p.139-167, 2002.13.	Sterman, J. D., Business Dynamics: Systems Thinking and Modeling for a Complex World, Boston, 2000.
              


