本所簡介　師資介紹　課程規劃　辦法規章　師生作品　論文摘要　表單下載　碩博士生　專題討論　特色計畫　相關連結




作者: 王賢吉  論文題目: 主題遊樂園永續經營系統動態模擬與分析－以劍湖山世界為例
【摘                要】

                    　　近年來，在國內掀起一股觀光休閒熱潮後，充滿多元化、科技化、驚險刺激性等等的主題式遊樂園相繼林立。由於主題式遊樂觀光產品的生命周期相對較短暫，經常 不得不面對經營慘淡的情況。在旅遊業管理者及決策者中，對於主題式遊樂觀光產品的多變性往往無法掌握，只能被動地從經驗法則中學習與瞭解，造成許多投資上的錯誤決策，同時也造成了環境與經濟上的雙重浪費，而無法達到永續經營之願景。因此，能夠全面總覽主題遊樂園各向度之成功經營因素，並瞭解旅遊市場中遊客 量的非線性變化，即成為旅遊業決策者所必定需要瞭解學習的重點工作，從被動地關註每年的遊客量轉為主動地去體認主題遊樂市場以創造高重遊率。主題遊樂園中許多經營與投資決策的有效性都取決於對旅遊產品的周期特性是否把握，如能理解主題遊樂園周期中的階段特性，則必然可減低投資上的錯誤決策。本研究的目的即 以永續經營與發展的理論思考觀光旅遊產品上做投資決策的問題，並以系統動態學(System Dynamics)為基礎，利用電腦軟體STELLA為工具，從系統思考的宏觀角度，以模糊德爾菲法篩選系統因子，建構出劍湖山世界永續經營系統動態學模型，模擬與分析旅遊產品市場的動態情境，瞭解企業經濟發展對於環境所造成的衝擊，試圖提出利於經營與管理之策略供劍湖山世界主題遊樂區經營管理業者參考，助其作出正確的發展決策。
關鍵字：系統動態學、主題遊樂園、永續經營

【ABSTRACT】

                    　　After a great fervour of tourism swept over, diversified, technological, adventurous, and …etc, various kinds of theme park come out and entertained out lift. Due to the passion to theme park is a relatively short, owner of theme park usually experienced difficulties to attract tourists to revisit and that result deficiency of profits. It is also hard to control variant unpredictable situations happen. The only way to avoid every kind of negative situation happen is to learn from the past. However, if any bad situation happened, it could cost great economic and geographical damages, consequently, bankruptcy would occur and the park would discontinue from operating.Therefore, in order to increase the percentage of revisiting, from passively concentrating on observing the statistic of tourist flow to actively understanding the tourism market, executives of theme park should study every essential element which can successfully help to operate and comprehend the non-linear flow of visitors. A lot operation and investment decisions are determined depended on assurance of periodical characteristic of tourist products. Once decision makers can understand the gradation of characteristic in each period, they can surely reduce mistakes during investment.This study is based on theoretical thought of continuing operating and development of tourist product to solve problems on investment decisions. 　　The study uses System Dynamics as basis, software “STELLA” as tool and from the system point of view build a continuing operation model to simulate and analyst the movement in the tourist market. Janfusun fancyworld theme park, for instance, uses Fuzzy Delphi to choice the variable and create a dynamic system model to explain operating and managing strategy for owner of Janfusun fancyworld theme park to make the right developing decision.






網頁維護人：吳宏基　TEL：+886-4-23323000-7156　FAX：+886-4-23742373　E-MAIL：dcollege@cyut.edu.tw









